{"id":947,"parent_id":946,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":947,"title":"Haggai 1","subtitle":"","short_title":"Hag.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/1","content":[["div",[".title",["span.dominant","Haggai"]],[".titleNumber","Chapter 1"],[".studySummary",["i","Haggai exhorts the people to build the temple."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/1.1","order":"02.38.001.62618"},["b","1"],"In",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"the second year"],"of Darius the king, in the sixth",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"month"],", in the first day of the month, came the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"by Haggai the prophet unto",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"Zerubbabel"],"the son of Shealtiel, governor of Judah, and to Joshua the son of Josedech, the high priest, saying,"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/1.2","order":"02.38.001.62619"},["b","2"],"Thus speaketh the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts, saying, This people say, The time is not come, the time that the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"’s house should be built."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/1.3","order":"02.38.001.62620"},["b","3"],"Then came the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"by Haggai the prophet, saying,"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/1.4","order":"02.38.001.62621"},["b","4"],["i","Is it"],"time for you, O ye, to dwell in your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"ceiled"],"houses, and this house",["i","lie"],"waste?"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/1.5","order":"02.38.001.62622"},["b","5"],"Now therefore thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts;",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"Consider"],"your ways."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/1.6","order":"02.38.001.62623"},["b","6"],"Ye have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"sown"],"much, and bring in little; ye",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"eat"],", but ye have not enough; ye drink, but ye are not filled with drink; ye clothe you, but there is none warm; and he that",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"earneth"],"wages earneth",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_6d"},"wages"],["i","to put it"],"into a bag with",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_6e"},"holes"],"."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/1.7","order":"02.38.001.62624"},["b","7"],"¶Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts;",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"Consider"],"your",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"ways"],"."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/1.8","order":"02.38.001.62625"},["b","8"],"Go up to the mountain, and bring wood, and build the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"house"],"; and I will take pleasure in it, and I will be glorified, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/1.9","order":"02.38.001.62626"},["b","9"],"Ye looked for much, and, lo,",["i","it came"],"to little; and when ye brought",["i","it"],"home, I did blow upon it. Why? saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts. Because of mine house that",["i","is"],"waste, and ye run every man unto his own house."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/1.10","order":"02.38.001.62627"},["b","10"],"Therefore the heaven over you is stayed from dew, and the earth is stayed",["i","from"],"her",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"fruit"],"."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/1.11","order":"02.38.001.62628"},["b","11"],"And I called for a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"drought"],"upon the land, and upon the mountains, and upon the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"corn"],", and upon the new wine, and upon the oil, and upon",["i","that"],"which the ground bringeth forth, and upon men, and upon cattle, and upon all the labour of the hands."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/1.12","order":"02.38.001.62629"},["b","12"],"¶Then Zerubbabel the son of Shealtiel, and Joshua the son of Josedech, the high priest, with all the remnant of the people, obeyed the voice of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"their God, and the words of Haggai the prophet, as the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"their God had",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"sent"],"him, and the people did fear before the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/1.13","order":"02.38.001.62630"},["b","13"],"Then spake Haggai the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"’s messenger in the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"’s message unto the people, saying, I",["i","am"],"with you, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/1.14","order":"02.38.001.62631"},["b","14"],"And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"stirred up the spirit of Zerubbabel the son of Shealtiel, governor of Judah, and the spirit of Joshua the son of Josedech, the high priest, and the spirit of all the remnant of the people; and they came and did work in the house of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts, their God,"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/1.15","order":"02.38.001.62632"},["b","15"],"In the four and twentieth day of the sixth month, in the second year of Darius the king."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/1.1a","order":"02.38.001.62633"},["b","1a"],"Probably 520",["span.small","B.C."],"Darius Hystaspes reigned 521–486",["span.small","B.C."]],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/1.1b","order":"02.38.001.62635"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.1,10.10,20"},"Hag. 2:1, 10 (10, 20)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/1.1c","order":"02.38.001.62637"},["b","1c"],"Grandson of Jehoiachin, former king of Judah.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/3.19.17-19"},"1 Chr. 3:19 (17–19)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezra/2.2.1-2"},"Ezra 2:2 (1–2)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/1.12.11-13"},"Matt. 1:12 (11–13)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/1.4a","order":"02.38.001.62639"},["b","4a"],["span.small","HEB"],"paneled."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/1.5a","order":"02.38.001.62641"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.18"},"Hag. 2:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/1.6a","order":"02.38.001.62643"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/28.38.38-40"},"Deut. 28:38 (38–40)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/micah/6.15"},"Micah 6:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/1.6b","order":"02.38.001.62645"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/9.20"},"Isa. 9:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"6c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/1.6c","order":"02.38.001.62647"},["b","6c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/family-managing-finances-in"},"TG Family, Managing Finances in"],"."],["div",{"id":"6d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/1.6d","order":"02.38.001.62649"},["b","6d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/wages"},"TG Wages"],"."],["div",{"id":"6e","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/1.6e","order":"02.38.001.62651"},["b","6e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/waste"},"TG Waste"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/1.7a","order":"02.38.001.62653"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/meditation"},"TG Meditation"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/1.7b","order":"02.38.001.62655"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.15"},"2 Pet. 2:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/1.8a","order":"02.38.001.62657"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezra/6.3"},"Ezra 6:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.119"},"D&C 88:119"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.3"},"95:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/1.10a","order":"02.38.001.62659"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/28.18"},"Deut. 28:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/1.11a","order":"02.38.001.62661"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/drought"},"TG Drought"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/famine"},"Famine"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/1.11b","order":"02.38.001.62663"},["b","11b"],["span.small","OR"],"grain."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/1.12a","order":"02.38.001.62665"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priesthood-authority"},"TG Priesthood, Authority"],"."]]}
